race.comment: MAN OF THE TOWN (2) is a lightly raced galloper and unbeaten from two starts this campaign, the latest over a mile at Eagle Farm. Regular rider back aboard and although up in weight is fitter again and can make it three straight. SCOUNDREL (7) gave a big start but came home strongly to finish fourth behind MAN OF THE TOWN last time. With the claim meets him 5.5kg better and should be at top now so can definitely turn the tables with the right run. FIFTH FORCE (5) resumed from a long break over 1400m at Eagle Farm and although missed the frame was close to the winner. Placed 2/3 when second-up and extra trip a huge plus. FORTY TIMES (9) has been a long time between wins but just missed last time and has placed three of last five. Has a nice weight for this. Will be running on hard.
